name: Diversify-project

# The DIVERSIFY-project organization

This Github organization hosts a set of prototypes that aim at investigating the engineering and emergence of software diversity in collaborative adaptive systems.
The work of this organization is supported by the FP7 STREP [DIVERSIFY project](http://diversify-project.eu/)
